column5: LOL ...read the comments below the video! I know I shouldn't laugh but a few there killed me.
He uses it like a pro though!  Is that some sort of Crappie?  It's a beast of a pan fish for a little rod like that!  Funny stuff.
kid clearly doesn't need a real rod. I think I'm going out to buy that setup this weekend.
Noticed a lot of the Michigan Dirty going on there.
